1) addmovies.php adds new movie by the admin
2) reviewlist.php is used for watching all reviews made on a particular movie. Here a logged in user can update his/her comment
3) userrating.php shows all rating and comments by current user
4) watchlist shows a list of movies the user wishes to watch
5) On movie page user can add movie to watchlist, view information from IMDB page via json fetch and view all youtube trailers and 
speacial video related to that movie on a list which is also done by json fetch
